name: Courtyard
states:
  - id: index
    description: >
      You are standing in the courtyard at night. The moon is high in the sky. A big tree in the center casts a dark shadow in the moonlight.

      To the west the clock room has been sealed shut with a metal gate.
    choices:
      - text: look at tree
        details: A tall oak tree stands in the middle of the courtyard. It casts a dark shadow in the moonlight.
